AMENDMENT III


 
  
 Section 1. Article IV, Elections, shall be amended to read: 
 

ARTICLE IV - ELECTIONS

 
 Section 1. Qualified voters shall be all members of the Bad River 
Band of Chippewa Indians 18 years of age or older, on the day of the 
election.
 
 

