AMENDMENT IV


Section 1. Article IV, Elections, shall be further amended by adding 
a subsection (a) to read as follows:
 
 

ARTICLE IV - ELECTIONS

 
 Section 1. (a) Qualified voters may vote in absentee by requesting an 
absentee ballot in writing from the election committee thirty (30) 
days prior to election day.
 
 

