AMENDMENT XXVIII


 
 Section 1, Article TV — MEETINGS — BYLAWS shall be amended to read 
as follows: 
 

ARTICLE VI - MEETINGS - BYLAWS


Section 1. Regular meetings of the Tribal Council shall be held on 
the first Wednesday of each month, and at such other times as the 
Tribal Council may by resolution provide. Called meetings -shall be
held at the discretion of the Chairman or upon request of three 
members of the Tribal Council. Three days written notice shall be 
given to all Council members.

All Tribal Council meetings shall be posted at least three days prior 
to a meeting. Signs to be placed in all public places within the 
exterior boundaries of the Bad River Reservation.

